Frostbite shakes her head to Darkfates question as she taps a few keys on her 
command console making a hologram of a massive metal sphere appear where the 
hologram was.

Frostbite: "No, I am only commanding this small amount of troops. (Now 
pointing to the hologram.)He.. is our master."
